WEBVTT

00:00:12.452 --> 00:00:21.797 line:90% position:50% align:center
Ever loyal to Jehovah,
Loyal love we wish to show.

00:00:21.797 --> 00:00:31.559 line:90% position:50% align:center
As a people, dedicated,
His commands we want to know.

00:00:31.559 --> 00:00:41.322 line:90% position:50% align:center
His advice will never fail us,
And his counsel we obey.

00:00:41.322 --> 00:00:51.042 line:90% position:50% align:center
He is loyal; we can trust him.
From his side we’ll never stray.

00:01:01.054 --> 00:01:10.566 line:90% position:50% align:center
Ever loyal to our brothers,
Sticking close in times of need.

00:01:10.566 --> 00:01:20.203 line:90% position:50% align:center
Ever caring, always trusting,
Ever kind in word and deed.

00:01:20.203 --> 00:01:29.840 line:90% position:50% align:center
We show honor to our brothers
And respect them from the heart.

00:01:29.840 --> 00:01:40.061 line:90% position:50% align:center
Ever loyal, ever closer,
From their side we’ll never part.

00:01:49.531 --> 00:01:59.085 line:90% position:50% align:center
Ever loyal to their guidance
When our brothers lead the way.

00:01:59.085 --> 00:02:08.638 line:90% position:50% align:center
When they give us clear direction,
May we loyally obey.

00:02:08.638 --> 00:02:18.651 line:90% position:50% align:center
Then the blessing from Jehovah
Will be ours to make us strong.

00:02:18.651 --> 00:02:29.330 line:90% position:50% align:center
When we’re loyal, ever faithful,
To Jehovah we’ll belong.

00:02:30.290 --> 00:02:39.009 line:90% position:50% align:center
To Jehovah we’ll belong.

